# 34th Army Corps (Russian Empire)

|allegiance=Imperial Russian Army
|battles = World War I
}}
The 34th Army Corps was an Army corps in the Imperial Russian Army.
Part of
*10th Army: 1915
*2nd Army: 1915
*1st Army: 1915 - 1916
*4th Army: 1916
*Russian Special Army: 1916 - 1917
*7th Army: 1917
Commanders
*January 22-July 2, 1917: Pavlo Skoropadskyi
